title: Historia siue descriptio plantarvm omnivm, tam domesticarvm qvam exoticarvm: earundem cum virtutes influentiales, elementares, et naturales, tum subtilitates, necnon icones ... proponens: atque una cum his partium omnium corporis humani ut externarum ita
author: Thurneisser zum Thurn, Leonhard, 1530?-1596
